      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEPUNGA DESTINY (4) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (30.40) at Sandown behind All I See in a Maiden. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. The form out of her last race has been franked. Good form should continue. SOLID GROOVE (7) is a Danielle Smith-trained newcomer by Collision out of All Too Easy with no trial form to work with. Respect any moves in the market. KING OF CHAOS (1) jumps from the inside draw. Last start finished 4th in a Maiden on April 13 over 515m at Sandown behind White Mocha beaten 7 lengths (30.29). Can feature with the right run. BAGEL (8) is by Fernando Bale out of Carla Veloso making debut. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can sneak into the frame with the right run.",
